[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Some academies stand out in terms of the drop in the %age of those who were statemented or on school action plus: 
[normal]Harris Academy, East Dulwich - 12.4%;
[normal]John Medejski Academy, -18.3%; 
[normal]Paddington Academy, -19.3%; 
[normal]Havelock Academy, -10.6%. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Those which stick out for an overall drop in special needs are: 
[normal]St Aidan's Academy, -21%; 
[normal]Harris Academy, South Norwood, -15%; 
[normal]Havelock Academy, - 15%; 
[normal]New Line Learning, - 12%.
